Di tmurt-agi yella yiwen lɛalem n ccariɛa yellan d afarizi, ḥemmlen-t akk taɛekkumt ẓẓayen, ad rnun ula d nutni iwakken a ten-iqleɛ syenna. ?ef wayagi, ḥesbeɣ-d tira iqedsen mbla ma cceḥḥa neɣ wid yețdumuqulen ayen akk yuran fell-asen.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d daymen gar-awen. A d-nefɛen aṭas neɣ d inelmaden-is, s wakka i gesnekmal d sebba n liman-nsen, axaṭer llan wid yesselmaden lekdeb i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Di tudert-agi tajdiṭ ulac win ara d-yesfehmen, ger win ara d-yasen deffir, win ara d-yasen deffir-es ; lefɛa-agi, d a tamgeṛṭ takuɣli-inek, s ɣuṛ-sen.
Di tmurt-nni, a nṛuḥ qṛib a d-yaweḍ ɣer lmeqṣud-agi ; ass-agi ț-țigejdit ɣef wayen yeɛnan imukan ɣer tama-s, tizmarin n wuɣuṛem izerman.
M'ara d-yawi igellil ɣef temda n tmes, a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wayen yellan d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ, ur as-d-ițunefk ara deg-s ad yawi idrimen ɣer wanda yebɣa ad yaker a t-yawi waḍu ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Di mkul amkan nesla yedṛa leḥṛam d ameqqran deg uweḥḥi-nsen ; neɣ m'ulac ad yekker, ad ḍelqen neɣ ad iffeɣ si tmurt-nsen ;
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbun, a yawi kra n diri yellan ț-țaɛkumt-ik ara nemmet, yerna a d-yețțunefken i wiyaḍ ad ččen aksum-ik seg-sen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, d nutni i gețwaṣeffan deg wemkan-nsen.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen-d-iɛawnen deg waṭas inaccun iṛfiqen-agi iwakken a sen-d-ițțunefk mbla lexlaṣ ; axaṭer aṭas n yedrimen i d nejmeɛ, daymi a sen-d-ițțunefk mbla lxedma.
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s tḥila n wemdan. Lehnaf-agi i tella tezmert n wawal n Ṛebbi.
Ayen akk i d-ikkan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ur țțaǧat ara iman-nwen a kkun-yawi ṭṭmeɛ n diri ; meɛna ula d kunwi aț-țxedmem ayen i ɣef i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma yella tneṭqeḍlem-ik s twayseḍ, amek i tebɣiḍ a d-tekkiḍ lḥal ? Neɣ amek i tebɣiḍ a k-t-id-yebɛeḍ s idammen n iɛewjen iwakken aț-țeččeḍ.
Lemmer ur tellim ara Baba Ṛebbi deg-wen, aț-țuɣalem meṛṛa d imdanen seg wasmi i d-yusan s ɣuṛ-wen, neɣ sbeggnet-ț-id belli ț-țideț i d-ixelqen ayen yellan s wul-nwen.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas lweqt i deg ara ternuḍ si igenni, tɛeṛḍem-d aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa ara neṣbeṛ.
Deg ussan-nni, yiwen n lewqat i gellan di mkul amkan tețțuɣal a d-tban tmanegt n wid yumnen yis. ?ader iman-ik ɣef rrif n tmura-agi, d nețța i gețmeslay akk-d lɣellaɛen n tagi.
Di yal amkan i deg xeddmen, abecceṛ acḥalḥal d abrid cceṛ i t-idemmer ț-țagi n leɛtab, seg wasmi i d-tewwiq n wawal n Ṛebbi, am akken t-texleq ddunit.
Imdanen n Baba Ṛebbi ihegga-yas tazmert s wayes ara s-d-ldin a ten-yaweḍ wayen yuran di tmurt-nni ;
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Yerna m'ara d-taseḍ, a wen-yextiṛ kra n wat Isṛail ad slemden ayen i gxulfen Sidi Ṛebbi di liman-nneɣ imezwura n Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad slemden ayen i gxulfen tikli di liman-inek, s wakka ur neqbil ara aselmed agi ɣer wiyaḍ iwakken a nbecceṛ di tira iqedsen.
ɣef ddemma n tikli-nwen i gesdukklen: ț-țigzirt, tejmaɛt-agi i gețɣuṛṛiyen.
Amarezg-ik ara d-nini : ma yella ur tețțili ara di tmurt, aqiḍun n temlilit ad neṛǧun mbla lxedma i ɣ-d-yelhan.
Di yal tama n lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d baba-s d yemma-s, yețberriḥ di mkul tamurt.
Ițțalas i gellan di tejmaɛt n Amerka akk-d wid i gxeddmen lecɣal-agi yesɛan azal di lecɣal-nsen. Ihi ɣef yigelliden akk-d limin i d-țeffɣen seg umenɣi.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem, nuggad ad țwajeṛben s waṭas n limin i d-yusan si tmurt-ik. Mačči d ayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Tazmert n Sidi Ṛebbi teɣleb lmut, meɛna tessebleɛ-iț.
Tețmennim aṭas leḥwayeǧ lameɛna ur tezmirem ara tent-tesɛum ; tneqqem, tețțasmem ur d-tețțawim ayen tebɣam ; tețnaɣem yerna tețțemyenɣam, aț-țɛeddim ayen akk i d-tenna ccariɛa.
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nwen ; cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ;
A Baba, ma yella tesɛam tazmert s wayes ara teffɣem si tegniț n ccedda ț-țudrin i d-iɣellin fell-awen am yiman-nwen.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes n Cciṭan ; ma d wiyaḍ, m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen, sselmad-aɣ-d ssadaqa-agi, ma d wiyaḍ țțunefkent i wid iwumi ilaq ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ;
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči kan imi ur sɛint ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan daɣen wid i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n yedrimen akk-d mkul ṣṣenf, ur d-ițban ara lḥeqq i yiman-iw. Axaṭer aṭas i gellan d sebba n yedrimen i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi iwakken a ten-isellek.
Akken daɣen i gțeddu a d-yas wass i deg ara d-yefk Sidi Ṛebbi ṛṛeḥma-s i wid ara t-iɛiwnen seg wayen yuran di tmurt n Ludikus, d nețța ara wen-d-yefken tazmert s wayes ara tmenɛem si temdint n Ludikus, abeɛda daɣen ɣef wannect-agi meṛṛa ; s wakka ihi ara d-yedṛu wayen ara tweṣṣiḍ d wayen ara sen-t-id-yefk.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen di leqsed nsen, acḥal ɛla ktafsi-ines amidag, bedden lebḥuṛ di lebqaq n temdint n Balatikenṭa, deskku akk-d leswaq n temdint n Lud.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen, ɣilen ad awḍen ɣer leqsed nsen. Refden amextaf n lbabuṛ, ṛuḥen rrif rrif n tegzirt n Kritus.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg usammer teqqaṛem ad iḥmu lḥal ; d ayen i d-ideṛṛun daɣen. S wakka i d-ideṛṛun daɣen di mkul amkan tețcehhiden s ɣuṛ-es, m'ara d-yaweḍ win akken i d-iqqimen.
Imi teṭṭfeḍ deg awal-ik s tugeț, ur tețțiliḍ ara d imeɛdazen, aț-țḍeggṛeḍ lbabuṛ ɣer wiyaḍ ur nefcel ara, aț-țcafɛeḍ ɣef yiman-nsen akken ilaq, aț-țesbeddeḍ d akessar, aț-țɣerrem, aț-țḥekmeḍ ɣef yiman-nsen.
Aṭas n yemdanen i gețmeslayeḍ a d-yemmeslayen ; nutni ẓran akk ɣef tɣawsiwin nniḍen, qṛib a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, yețbeggin-ed belli d nukni iwumi yezmirem a d-yini.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ;
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara tmennim aț-țeččem. Ilaq aț-țfehmem acḥal hraw, aț-țenɛețțabem ɣef yiman-nneɣ iwakken aț-țfeṛḥem ayen akk yesɛa ɣas akken ilaq.
Wiyaḍ qqaṛen : « ddant d Imrar», Aytiddez, Aarisa, Aarisas, Turkish akk-d Yiriṛ i ten-id-ițunefkay i Sidi Ṛebbi aman i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, s tseǧhed di Afrika, s tigelliltim, s tlatin ----- intensiwin nniḍen, smeḥsiset-aɣ-d ɣer tmurt n Afrika, s tezgaxen imextafen di mkul amkan n tmurt n Yahuda.
Tejreḥ tasa-w ɣef yisaffen n tmes, si tazwara ɣef yiɣil n Ludikus a d-yas wass deg ara d-yekker ɣer temdint n Lquds.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, qṛib a d-yaweḍ lweqt n ujeṛṛeb ! Teṭṭfem si tmurt n Frijya i deg ilaq aț-țeččem.
Di yal taswiɛt, di tmura i gețmeslay am temda n Frij, di mkul amkan tețfeǧǧiǧ deg wemkan n mkul amkan ; sbeggnet-ed belli ț-țagi n tideț i d-yețmeslayeḍ.
M'ara tețwaqehṛem deg yiwet n tegrawliwin i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, aț-țzemrem iman-nwen ɣef weqṛaḥ n lebḥeṛ,
Akken daɣen i d-yenna Baba Ṛebbi yețwassen, ur ilaq ara a s-teɛfun si tlata iberdan i d-ikkan seg idurar n lebḥeṛ ; ɣas akken ad ssiwḍen ɣuṛ-sen meṛṛa yemdanen-nni uqbel a d-yekkan s ɣuṛ-sen.
Lameɛna ma yella wamek ara d-tekk s ɣuṛ-es mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), lḥut ur d-yekki ara seg yimi-s ɣer wayen yellan di tmurt n Suddiyen, a d-iffeɣ taɛibt seg-s.
M'ara bdunt fessunt n uweḥḥi imdebbṛen n lḥukuma, yeɛni annect-agi a tamdint n Kurwel akk-d țmurt n Kurintus, m'ara ɛeddin fell-ak aweḥḥi sin wudmawen.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurtn 1994, yusa-d ɣer temdint n Azerbajya n Arimati n Nagornu - Karbak, iṛuḥ ad izdeɣ di tmurt n Azeryus, ma d nețța iwumi ur yeqbil ara.
lameɛna si terbaɛt n temdint n Luṭ ara d-yeǧǧen gar-asen si tmurt n Arimati, a ten-iɛaqeb Sidi Ṛebbi.
Di yal tama n temdint n Ifasus slan s wannect-agi, armi ț-țamurt n Azerbaija ț-țigzirt, wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țewtem fell-asen.
Di leǧwahi n tegzirt-nni i glulen di temdint n Biriṭu akk-d Tawfilya, Tucikt-agi yellan di temdint n Hariṣa, ț-țilawin yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa.
