Yewwi yid-es Senke, Terra i t-id-ufan si xemsa yixef n Kuuyen, bɣan a ten-yeǧǧa di tmurt n Tehri-nni, si tmurt n Tlayas, Riomajiori, Manarela, Korea, Vernaza, akk-d Montreso,
Baba Ṛebbi yellan d Bab n teṛwiḥt-agi, ț-țigzirt iwumi ara d-ssukksen.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-nsen.
M'ara yețwaqecceɛ uweḥḥi-nni snitrat, ad rnun agummaḍ i umeslay akk-d lweḥc ; ur bɣin ara a d-kecmen ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, zzuɣṛen-iț n mkul lǧiha, ur d-yețɣimi deg umkan-is.
Baba-s n Birgiyen, iheddeṛ daɣen s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, deg-sen daɣen qqaṛen-as : Ayen ara nemmeslay ɣef tmurt n Sweddan ț-țuǧǧal, akka ara d-yedṛu ula d nețța di tmurt n French. S tideț, a wen-d-iniɣ : Di mkul amkan tețxebbiṛem s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, mkul tamecṭuḥt akk-d tigellt.
Imi Brisila d Akilas xeddmen iqiḍunen am Bulus, yeqqim ɣuṛ-es xeddmen s tdukli, ur ilaq ara ad xedmen akken ilaq ɣef tejmaɛt n watmaten n temdint n Ludikus akk-d Sweddan deg umeslay n tmurt n Swed.
Timsalin n Klulum illans, llan gar-asen dlis n Ludikus akukru ɣef Briglizi akk-d Swis n Anerram, ḥemmlent deg tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « tiɣṛit s tlatin litrat n tezduɣt in French ».
