Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiḍaṛṛen-nneɣ, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Akken daɣen i glaq aț-țxelṣem tabzert i lḥukuma, mmi-s n tamtunt ( iɣes ), țḥebbiṛet ɣef wannect-agi.
